data.description:
WoodSpring Suites is a collection of nearly 300 affordable extended stay hotels across the United States. Proudly a part of Choice Hotels International, headquartered in North Bethesda, Maryland.

WoodSpring Suites hotels offer oversized guestrooms, all with in-room kitchens, free WiFi, 24/7 access to guest laundry rooms, vending machines, and staff support. Many hotels are 100% smoke-free and offer pet-friendly accommodations.

WoodSpring Suites are extended stay hotels for good people with practical needs, down-to-earth attitudes and a comfortable style, and who appreciate the value of life’s necessities – done really well. 

Our hotels and weekly rates and monthly rates are designed with longer-stay guests in mind. Business travelers, military members, traveling medical professionals, vacationers, seasonal travelers, those relocating, and individuals, couples, and small families temporarily displaced from their homes will all fee comfortable and at home while our guest. 

For more information on our hotels, visit woodspring.com/ourbrand. To learn more about franchise opportunities visit choicehotelsdevelopment.com. For support or other questions visit woodspring.com/company/contact.
